  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You may spend a superiority die targeting one allied creature within 30 feet of you. </p><p>When you do, the next time they would make an attack of any type, they add twice the result to their damage roll. </p><p>On a successful hit of the allied creatures attack, if you make the same type of attack, targeting the same creature, on your next turn, you add the same damage to your damage roll</p>",
